        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>The collection consists of twenty-four handwritten letters written in Spain. Most are from Smith to his girlfriend, identified only as "Jeanette." One is from Smith to his sister(?) Clara, and one from a friend and fellow volunteer, Harry "Jack" Boxer, to "Jeanette." Three items are undated fragments. Several of Harold Smith's original letters are accompanied by typed transcripts.</p>
        </scopecontent>
